OL,3,CHow a university scholarship became a
OL,4,Cbeacon of hope for one man from Gaza
OL,6,FA group of around 40 Palestinian
OL,7,Fstudents with places to study at UK
OL,8,Funiversities have arrived to begin
OL,9,Ftheir studies after being evacuated
OL,10,Ffrom Gaza. ITV News Correspondent Neil
OL,11,FConnery spoke with one student before
OL,12,Fthe ceasefire between Israel and Hamas
OL,13,Fhad been announced.
OL,15,FThe contrast couldn't be greater. The
OL,16,Fserene calm of a Glasgow library is a
OL,17,Fworld away from the horror of Gaza
OL,18,Fthat Mohammed has endured over the
OL,19,Fpast two years.
