OL,3,CHow a university scholarship became a
OL,4,Cbeacon of hope for one man from Gaza
OL,6,FInside, one of a handful of Gaza
OL,7,Fstudents helped by the UK government
OL,8,Fto come here and study tells me of his
OL,9,Fnew home two weeks after arriving.
OL,11,F"I think Glasgow is really amazing,
OL,12,Fand you have a supporting community.
OL,13,FIt's all good here... except the
OL,14,Fweather," he laughs.
OL,16,FMohammed was in a displacement camp in
OL,17,FGaza when he found out he'd won a
OL,18,FChevening Scholarship.
