OL,3,CHow a university scholarship became a
OL,4,Cbeacon of hope for one man from Gaza
OL,6,FMohammed says he learned his family
OL,7,Fhome in Gaza City has now been
OL,8,Fcompletely destroyed. He shows me a
OL,9,Fvideo of the scene.
OL,11,F"We are seeing my house and my
OL,12,Fneighbours' houses. It's very hard to
OL,13,Fsee," he said, pausing and looking
OL,14,Faway.
OL,16,FHe lives in constant fear for his
OL,17,Ffamily left behind.
