OL,3,CHow a university scholarship became a
OL,4,Cbeacon of hope for one man from Gaza
OL,6,F"You are hearing air strikes near and
OL,7,Fyour brother or father is out and
OL,8,Fyou're wondering is it near to them or
OL,9,Fnot," he said.
OL,11,F"They are experiencing that every day."
OL,13,FMohammed is determined to return to
OL,14,Fput his studies and knowledge to good
OL,15,Fuse to help those in Gaza.
